WEBVTT

00:00.414 --> 00:06.061
We use "a few" for countable nouns and "a little" for uncountable nouns.

00:09.626 --> 00:11.246
How many cats do you have?

00:15.059 --> 00:16.991
I have a few cats.

00:21.009 --> 00:22.960
There are a few dogs in my home.

00:26.812 --> 00:28.329
She has a few apples.

00:31.959 --> 00:33.705
I need a little water.

00:37.423 --> 00:39.603
Just add a little salt.

00:43.212 --> 00:45.886
How much sugar do you take in your coffee?

00:49.356 --> 00:51.473
Stop! That's too much.

00:55.213 --> 00:56.773
I only want a little.

